cs.SY, cs.CR, cs.AI, cs.NI, cs.SE 

This paper deals with false data injection attacks in power systems, which is a topic related to control systems (cs.SY) and cybersecurity (cs.CR). The use of predictive filters to detect these attacks involves machine learning techniques (cs.AI) and signal processing (cs.NI). Finally, the paper also discusses the potential consequences of these attacks on the power system, which falls under software engineering (cs.SE).
